## Current

* Keep content of any form in [[tanks|tank]] with customizable access
  control and a full-featured [[API]].
* Use a tank as a simple [[markdown]] [[wiki|Using Wikis]] with
  [[backlinks]], transclusion and inter-tank links.
* [[Compose|composition]] a tank with applications such as [TiddlyWiki
  Classic](http://classic.tiddlywiki.com/) and [TiddlyWiki
  Five](http://tiddlywiki.com/), including building custom apps.
* [[Move|mover]] [[tiddlers|tiddler]] between tanks.
* Host [[single page applications|Single Page Apps]] that use the
  [[API]].
* Atom feeds of content in tanks.
* Login using [GitHub](https://github.com/).
* SSL Everywhere.
* [[Websocket-based|websockets]] in-browser notifications.
* Server side rendering of tw classic wikitext.

## Planned

* Prettiness!
* Server side rendering of tw five wikitext.
* Additional applications for comps.
* Custom access control editor.
* Login using other services (e.g. facebook).

